  "remarks": "\nSergey Alexandrovich KULIKOV has been Head and Chairman of the Management Board at Rusnano, a Russian investment entity affiliated to the Government of Russia. In his position, KULIKOV was working as a director or equivalent in a Government of Russia-affiliated entity. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
